      CLEARWATER ROOF REPAIR<br/><span class="gt">EMERGENCY SERVICE</span>
    </h1>
    <p class="max-w-2xl mx-auto" style="color:#555555;font-size:1.05rem;line-height:1.75">
      Happy Roof provides fast, reliable roof repair in Clearwater. Whether it is storm damage on Clearwater Beach, a leak in Countryside, or worn-out flashing in Skycrest, we respond quickly with honest assessments and quality workmanship.
    </p>
    <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-3 justify-center mt-8">
      <a href="/contact" class="btn-t">Get a Free Estimate <svg width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.5"><path d="M5 12h14"/><path d="m12 5 7 7-7 7"/></svg></a>
      <a href="tel:8135957663" class="btn-o call-tracking-number">Call (813) 595-7663</a>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- INFO STRIP -->
<div style="background:#FFFFFF;border-top:2px solid #E6A817;border-bottom:1px solid #E0E0E0;padding:.85rem 0">
  <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-5">
    <div class="flex flex-wrap items-center justify-center gap-x-8 gap-y-2 font-display font-bold text-sm tracking-widest" style="color:#1A1A1A;text-transform:uppercase;font-family:'Barlow Condensed',sans-serif">
      <span>Clearwater, FL</span><span style="color:#E6A817">·</span><span>CCC1337380</span><span style="color:#E6A817">·</span><span>HappyRoof.com</span><span style="color:#E6A817">·</span><span style="color:#3B9FD9">(813) 595-7663</span>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

<!-- WHY SECTION -->
<section class="py-20" style="background:#FFFFFF">
  <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-5">
    <div class="grid lg:grid-cols-2 gap-14 items-start">
      <div>
        <p class="sl gt mb-3">Why Choose Happy Roof for Repairs</p>
        <h2 style="font-family:'Barlow Condensed',sans-serif;font-weight:800;font-size:clamp(2rem,4vw,3rem);line-height:.95;color:#1A1A1A;letter-spacing:-.01em;margin-bottom:1.5rem">WHY CLEARWATER HOMEOWNERS TRUST US FOR ROOF REPAIRS</h2>
        <p style="color:#555555;font-size:1rem;line-height:1.75;margin-bottom:1.5rem">Clearwater's barrier island geography puts it directly in the path of Gulf storms. When tropical systems make landfall or pass nearby, Clearwater Beach, Island Estates, and Sand Key take the full force of storm surge and wind. Even the mainland neighborhoods - Countryside, Skycrest, and the communities along Drew Street - experience damaging gusts and torrential rain that can expose weaknesses in aging roofs.</p>
        <p style="color:#555555;font-size:1rem;line-height:1.75;margin-bottom:1.5rem">The most frequent repairs we see in Clearwater include wind-damaged shingles on the 1970s and 1980s ranch homes near Countryside Mall, cracked barrel tiles on the Mediterranean-style homes of Harbor Oaks and Belleair Bluffs, and corroded flashing on beachside properties where salt air attacks metal components year-round. Pipe boot failures are another common issue, especially on homes 15+ years old, where the rubber seal around plumbing vents dries out and cracks in Clearwater's intense sun.</p>
        <p style="color:#555555;font-size:1rem;line-height:1.75;margin-bottom:1.5rem">Happy Roof provides fast, honest repairs throughout Clearwater. If a repair will solve the problem, we recommend a repair - not a replacement. For active leaks, we offer emergency tarping to protect your home while a permanent fix is scheduled. See all our Clearwater services at our <a href="/clearwater-roofing" style="color:#3B9FD9;text-decoration:none;font-weight:600">Clearwater roofing page</a> or visit our <a href="/roof-repair" style="color:#3B9FD9;text-decoration:none;font-weight:600">roof repair page</a>.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="space-y-4">
        <div class="scard p-6">
          <div class="check"><div class="check-dot"><svg width="10" height="10" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="#E6A817" stroke-width="3"><path d="M20 6L9 17l-5-5"/></svg></div><div><strong style="font-family:'Barlow Condensed',sans-serif;font-weight:700;font-size:1.05rem">Emergency Leak Response</strong><p style="color:#555555;font-size:.9rem;line-height:1.6;margin-top:.25rem">Same-day emergency tarping for active leaks in Clearwater. We stop the water intrusion immediately, then schedule a permanent repair.</p></div></div>
        </div>
        <div class="scard p-6">
          <div class="check"><div class="check-dot"><svg width="10" height="10" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="#E6A817" stroke-width="3"><path d="M20 6L9 17l-5-5"/></svg></div><div><strong style="font-family:'Barlow Condensed',sans-serif;font-weight:700;font-size:1.05rem">Storm & Wind Damage</strong><p style="color:#555555;font-size:.9rem;line-height:1.6;margin-top:.25rem">Clearwater's Gulf-facing location makes it vulnerable to tropical storms. We repair all wind and storm damage and help with insurance documentation.</p></div></div>
        </div>
        <div class="scard p-6">
          <div class="check"><div class="check-dot"><svg width="10" height="10" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="#E6A817" stroke-width="3"><path d="M20 6L9 17l-5-5"/></svg></div><div><strong style="font-family:'Barlow Condensed',sans-serif;font-weight:700;font-size:1.05rem">Coastal Corrosion Repair</strong><p style="color:#555555;font-size:.9rem;line-height:1.6;margin-top:.25rem">Salt air from the Gulf corrodes metal flashing, fasteners, and vents on Clearwater Beach and Island Estates homes. We replace failing components with marine-grade materials.</p></div></div>
        </div>
        <div class="scard p-6">
          <div class="check"><div class="check-dot"><svg width="10" height="10" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="#E6A817" stroke-width="3"><path d="M20 6L9 17l-5-5"/></svg></div><div><strong style="font-family:'Barlow Condensed',sans-serif;font-weight:700;font-size:1.05rem">Repair-vs-Replace Honesty</strong><p style="color:#555555;font-size:.9rem;line-height:1.6;margin-top:.25rem">If a targeted repair will protect your Clearwater home for years to come, that is what we recommend. We do not push replacements when repairs make sense.</p></div></div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- WHAT'S INCLUDED / COMMON REPAIRS / WHAT WE CHECK -->
<section class="py-20" style="background:#F7F7F7">
