        </div>
        <h3 style="font-family:'Barlow Condensed',sans-serif;font-weight:800;font-size:1.35rem;color:#1A1A1A;margin-bottom:.75rem">Cracked & Broken Tile</h3>
        <p style="color:#555555;font-size:.95rem;line-height:1.7">Barrel and flat tiles on Clearwater homes crack from debris impact and thermal stress. We source matching tiles and properly reseat them to prevent leaks.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="scard p-8">
        <div style="width:52px;height:52px;border-radius:14px;display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;background:rgba(230,168,23,.1);margin-bottom:1rem">
          <svg width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="#E6A817" stroke-width="2"><path d="M22 11.08V12a10 10 0 1 1-5.93-9.14"/><polyline points="22 4 12 14.01 9 11.01"/></svg>
        </div>
        <h3 style="font-family:'Barlow Condensed',sans-serif;font-weight:800;font-size:1.35rem;color:#1A1A1A;margin-bottom:.75rem">Pipe Boot & Flashing Failure</h3>
        <p style="color:#555555;font-size:.95rem;line-height:1.7">Rubber pipe boots dry out fast in Clearwater's sun. Flashing around chimneys and skylights deteriorates. We replace failing seals and flashing to stop leaks at their source.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- OUR PROCESS -->
<section class="py-20" style="background:#FFFFFF">
  <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-5">
    <div class="text-center mb-14">
      <p class="sl gt mb-3">How It Works</p>
      <h2 style="font-family:'Barlow Condensed',sans-serif;font-weight:800;font-size:clamp(2rem,4vw,3rem);line-height:.95;color:#1A1A1A;letter-spacing:-.01em">OUR REPAIR PROCESS</h2>
